motactic precision. More generally, our results\nillustrate how limits on sensory precision can be used to understand the\nlocation, spatial extent, and lifespan of bacterial behavioral responses in\necologically relevant environments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 19 May 2019 17:02:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-21"}
